<add><ab facs="#facs_226_line_1576748911884_8272">vnd <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> ſey Jm </ab><ab facs="#facs_226_line_1576748914348_8277">derſelb <expan>Eglolfſtein<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_226_line_1576748916904_8282">cʒü <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒeit </ab><ab facs="#facs_226_line_1576748918678_8287">vnd auch <expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> vor </ab><ab facs="#facs_226_line_1576748920495_8292">noch nach nye </ab><ab facs="#facs_226_line_1576748923819_8297">ıhtes ſchuldig </ab><ab facs="#facs_226_line_1576748925669_8302">geweſen / </ab></add> vnd dein <expan>vat<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd di <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beten Jn / daʒ er das </ab>
